This project is a Password Generator Application developed using Python.
It generates strong and random passwords based on user preferences such as length and complexity.

Project Objective

The main goal of this project is to create a secure password generator that helps users generate strong passwords to improve online security.

Features

User can specify the desired password length

Option to choose password complexity:

Letters only

Letters and Numbers

Letters, Numbers, and Symbols

Generates secure and random passwords

Simple and beginner-friendly Python implementation

Technologies Used

Python

random module

string module

How It Works

The user enters the desired password length.

The user selects the password complexity.

The program generates a random password using the selected character set.

The generated password is displayed on the screen.

Use Case

This project demonstrates the use of Python libraries for randomization and string handling while building a practical cybersecurity-related tool.
